high_descs: Turn around and veer right to the white table in the corner.
Pick up the potato on the table.
Turn around and veer left to the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Turn around and veer left, back to the white table.
Place the potato on the table, to the left of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated potato on a table.

high_descs: Heat the potato in the microwave.
Grab the potato back and go back to the table.
Place the potato back on the table.
anns.task_desc: Heat the potato and place it back on the table.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the wall, hang a right and go to the white table where the potato is.
Pick up the potato that is on the table.
Turn to the right, go forward, hang a right and go to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and turn it on, remove the potato once it is cooked.
Turn to the right, go to the wall, hang a right and go to the white table.
Put the potato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato on the table.
